: 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[555,587,1767,1784]" pageId="28" pageNumber="589">A-E</emphasis>
, branch tangential section showing autozooecial chambers and apertures,holotype CEGH-UNC 27508 a; 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[132,143,1790,1807]" pageId="28" pageNumber="589">F</emphasis>
